The way, the best way I can describe it is, and it does, it's weird is that it's if someone's

2573
02:13:47,280 --> 02:13:52,900
putting like one of those like cooking funnels in my right ear and they're giving me, there's

2574
02:13:52,900 --> 02:13:54,300
pouring in pure information.

2575
02:13:54,300 --> 02:13:55,480
It's not words.

2576
02:13:55,480 --> 02:13:59,020
It's just like intelligence, pure intelligence.

2577
02:13:59,020 --> 02:14:00,160
And I just know it.

2578
02:14:00,160 --> 02:14:04,000
And it's not male or female, but it's like, it's an order.

2579
02:14:04,080 --> 02:14:08,180
It's like, oh, I feel like that moment I'm a Manchurian candidate and something is speaking

2580
02:14:08,180 --> 02:14:09,340
to me in a higher language.

2581
02:14:09,700 --> 02:14:11,140
And I just understand it.

2582
02:14:11,140 --> 02:14:12,400
And it's like, I'm right here.

2583
02:14:13,380 --> 02:14:14,240
Where is here?

2584
02:14:14,240 --> 02:14:14,700
I don't.

2585
02:14:14,800 --> 02:14:19,080
So I lower the paper and there's a woman standing at the foot of my bed.

2586
02:14:19,780 --> 02:14:20,220
What?

2587
02:14:21,280 --> 02:14:23,500
And not great.

2588
02:14:23,500 --> 02:14:27,940
Um, but she's translucent, but three-dimensional.

2589
02:14:28,660 --> 02:14:34,340
So I can see her full body and, but I can also see through her and she's in like kind

2590
02:14:34,340 --> 02:14:42,540
of a tattered sundress and she's got long stringy blonde hair, but it's her eyes that

2591
