2618
02:16:26,640 --> 02:16:27,960
And again, it's a command.

2619
02:16:27,960 --> 02:16:33,420
It's like, I, then I must just look away with all the strength I can muster.

2620
02:16:33,420 --> 02:16:37,500
I turn until I'm not looking at the eyes and it's gone.

2621
02:16:37,500 --> 02:16:39,960
And you know what my first reaction was?

2622
02:16:40,700 --> 02:16:41,660
Come back.

2623
02:16:43,260 --> 02:16:49,060
The reason was, is because I have never felt so alive in my life.

2624
02:16:49,160 --> 02:16:54,580
I felt like if you just took two fingers and put them into an electrical socket, you're supercharged.

2625
02:16:54,820 --> 02:16:56,280
I was looking around the room.

2626
02:16:56,540 --> 02:16:59,780
I could look at the stucco and like, was like looking into the Grand Canyon.

2627
02:16:59,960 --> 02:17:01,200
