And I'm thinking, okay, I did not see his mouth move.

2710
02:21:41,520 --> 02:21:43,080
First of all, how's he know my name?

2711
02:21:43,560 --> 02:21:45,380
Secondly, I did not see his mouth move.

2712
02:21:45,740 --> 02:21:48,020
And I was like, hello.

2713
02:21:48,020 --> 02:21:53,040
And he said, turn around and walk the other way.

2714
02:21:55,440 --> 02:21:59,480
And he, mouth not moving and he's not, but he's not looking threatening.

2715
02:22:00,540 --> 02:22:03,860
And I kind of was like, got it on it.

2716
02:22:04,260 --> 02:22:05,460
Turn and I walk away.

2717
02:22:05,660 --> 02:22:07,640
And now I'm getting a little bit freaked out.

2718
02:22:07,720 --> 02:22:09,940
I get a waist down and I look back and he's not there anymore.

2719
02:22:10,300 --> 02:22:11,800
Was he tall, blonde?

2720
02:22:11,960 --> 02:22:12,200
Yes.

2721
02:22:12,300 --> 02:22:13,720
But he was further down the hill.

2722
02:22:13,720 --> 02:22:17,200
So I didn't have a chance to like look him in the eye and like I'm six, four.

2723
02:22:17,300 --> 02:22:20,400
So I didn't have a chance to look at him and say, oh, this guy's seven, two or whatever.

2724
02:22:20,860 --> 02:22:26,100
But he was well put together, like a specimen, like an absolute specimen.

2725
02:22:26,380 --> 02:22:30,760
So I asked, my friend comes back and I say, okay, I just had a really weird experience.

2726
02:22:30,840 --> 02:22:32,760
He goes, oh, with one of those tall white people.

2727
02:22:33,220 --> 02:22:35,780
I'm like, what do you know about them?

2728
02:22:35,780 --> 02:22:39,200
And he goes, they have a compound on the Orcas Island.

2729
02:22:39,200 --> 02:22:45,580
And he said, there's a lot of weird people that have compounds here because there's weird energy that comes like every couple, you know, months.

2730
02:22:46,020 --> 02:22:51,700
And they come in a black helicopter unmarked to a facility that's all gated and there's about eight of them.

2731
02:22:51,840 --> 02:22:54,700
And they come here and they stay here for a couple days at a time.

2732
02:22:55,000 --> 02:22:59,100
Apparently when this energy is really high and they get recharged.

2733
02:23:00,380 --> 02:23:00,580
Whoa.

2734
02:23:00,580 --> 02:23:03,340
And I'm like, have you ever met them?

2735
