He goes, there's a story about a number of years ago.

2738
02:23:10,320 --> 02:23:14,280
One of them came down into one of the pubs, right?

2739
02:23:14,300 --> 02:23:18,360
And just walked through the door one day and said, I want to have a drink.

2740
02:23:18,500 --> 02:23:19,980
And everyone's like, who are you?

2741
02:23:20,000 --> 02:23:21,640
And he's like, I live up the way.

2742
02:23:21,720 --> 02:23:22,840
And they're like, okay, cool.

2743
02:23:22,860 --> 02:23:24,800
And he's like, so what's it like to live here?

2744
02:23:24,820 --> 02:23:25,780
And they're like, on Orcas?

2745
02:23:25,860 --> 02:23:26,980
And he goes, no, on earth.

2746
02:23:28,480 --> 02:23:28,880
What?

2747
02:23:28,880 --> 02:23:33,820
And everyone was like, okay, dude, what is, what is going on here?

2748
02:23:33,840 --> 02:23:37,020
And then he had a couple of drinks and people had to like get him outside.

2749
02:23:37,020 --> 02:23:38,140
And he's like, no, it's okay.

2750
02:23:38,140 --> 02:23:39,580
I'll walk home, you know?

2751
02:23:39,580 --> 02:23:40,520
And then he left.

2752
02:23:40,620 --> 02:23:43,680
And so there's now, is that urban legend on Orcas?

2753
02:23:43,960 --> 02:23:45,860
Like this was like.

2754
02:23:45,920 --> 02:23:47,860
Is it like a pretty prevalent urban legend?

2755
02:23:47,860 --> 02:23:47,880
Yes.

2756
02:23:47,880 --> 02:23:48,180
Yes.

2757
02:23:48,260 --> 02:23:50,820
I mean, people, I mean, you ask almost anyone that lives on there.

2758
02:23:50,860 --> 02:23:54,640
It's like, oh, those, those tall white people, like they come here and, but they're very

2759
02:23:54,640 --> 02:23:54,940
private.

2760
02:23:55,040 --> 02:23:57,960
They don't intermingle with people, but there's a lot.

2761
02:23:57,960 --> 02:23:58,660
I have a cousin.

2762
02:23:58,760 --> 02:23:59,960
I was telling you who moved there.

2763
02:24:00,040 --> 02:24:03,240
I got to ask him about the tall white Nordic aliens.

2764
02:24:03,500 --> 02:24:03,620
Yeah.

2765
02:24:04,300 --> 02:24:08,580
So circling this all back to disclosure day, it's like, you know, one of the things that

2766
02:24:08,580 --> 02:24:14,320
Bryce and I talked about after we saw it was Spielberg told a really compelling story

2767
02:24:14,320 --> 02:24:15,540
about gray aliens.

2768
02:24:15,540 --> 02:24:18,920
That was not a human being.

2769
02:24:19,300 --> 02:24:19,920
I don't know.

2770
02:24:19,980 --> 02:24:20,880
It could have been a hybrid.

2771
02:24:21,300 --> 02:24:23,880
So maybe not a true, like extraterrestrial.

2772
02:24:24,200 --> 02:24:25,580
Maybe it was an ultra terrestrial.

2773
02:24:25,680 --> 02:24:29,440
Maybe it was like someone from Atlantis or, you know, what, there's so many theories around

2774
02:24:29,440 --> 02:24:29,940
the Nordics.

2775
02:24:30,080 --> 02:24:32,800
I don't know, but that was not just a good looking man.

2776
02:24:33,040 --> 02:24:35,040
